# Office binary formats — never let autocrlf or any text filter touch
# these. Git can autodetect most binaries but Windows/macOS clients
# occasionally disagree, and a single CRLF substitution in the middle
# of an .xlsm ZIP stream corrupts the whole workbook.
*.xlsm binary
*.xlsx binary
*.xlsb binary
*.xltm binary
*.xltx binary
*.xls  binary

# PDF too — same logic.
*.pdf  binary

# Keep PowerShell + .bas as text so diffs are sane.
*.ps1  text
*.bas  text
*.md   text
